zi iz, heyst, zi iz yinger fun mir mit a dray yor, umgefer aza gatung.

39
00:02:46,955 --> 00:02:48,840
nayntsn tsen, mer-veyniker.

40
00:02:48,480 --> 00:02:50,505
umgefer aza gatung. ikh ken nisht

41
00:02:50,465 --> 00:02:54,004
