in toyznt nayn hundert zeks.

44
00:02:55,181 --> 00:02:56,349
vu, oykhet in...?

45
00:02:56,129 --> 00:02:57,461
oykh in SATU MARE.

46
00:02:57,468 --> 00:03:01,361
yetst zayt zhe azoy gut, nisht vartndik oyf frages,

47
00:03:00,461 --> 00:03:01,578
yo, yo.

48
00:03:01,383 --> 00:03:11,149
dertseylt mir gants fray, vos ir gedenkt fun ayer kinder-yorn, vi se hot zikh gelebt in SATU MARE amolike yorn, biz se hot zikh ongehoybn di (tsores).

49
00:03:09,078 --> 00:03:10,050
amolike yorn.

50
00:03:10,712 --> 00:03:11,419
NACHON.

51
