di zakh iz azoy:

52
00:03:13,361 --> 00:03:16,822
s'ershte vil ikh zogn az ven ikh bin geboyrn gevorn

53
00:03:16,915 --> 00:03:18,961
iz deys geven nisht SATU MARE,

54
00:03:19,035 --> 00:03:21,283
nor deys iz geven Estraykh-Ungarn.

55
00:03:21,350 --> 00:03:23,830
deys hot geheysn SZATMÁRNÉMETI.

56
00:03:23,984 --> 00:03:26,944
dos heyst, Daytshe Satmer hot es geheysn,

57
00:03:27,026 --> 00:03:30,715
vayl ikh bin nokh geboyrn gevorn vos s'iz geven Ungarn,

58
00:03:30,768 --> 00:03:33,850
vayl nokh der tsvey- nokh der ershter velt-milkhome

59
00:03:33,910 --> 00:03:35,850
iz deys hersht gevorn ROMÁNIA.

60
00:03:36,241 --> 00:03:41,295
dos heyst, biz vi lang di milkhome hot gehaltn fun toyznt nayn hundert fertsn

61
00:03:41,433 --> 00:03:45,055
biz akhtsn iz dos alts nokh gevezn ungarn.

62
00:03:45,149 --> 00:03:48,231
hitst iz azoy: azoy vi di milkhome hot oysgebrokhn,

63
00:03:48,350 --> 00:03:50,772
hot men ale yunge mentshn ayngerufn.

64
00:03:50,846 --> 00:03:53,508
un mayn foter iz oykh geven tsishn deye.

65
00:03:53,674 --> 00:03:55,849
un ikh gedenk im azoy vi fun a kholem,

66
00:03:56,049 --> 00:04:01,805
nor deys eyne mol gedenk ikh im, ven er hot zikh fun mir gezegnt un iz avekgeforn in militer.

67
00:04:03,026 --> 00:04:04,880
nu, azoy vi er iz avekgeforn

68
00:04:05,065 --> 00:04:08,458
iz mayn IMA geblibn aleyn, in der heym.

69
00:04:08,600 --> 00:04:13,693
s'iz geven taken, der SABA hot gevoynt dortn un di SAVTA.

70
00:04:13,769 --> 00:04:16,749
ze'mir nisht geven oyf der gas, vayl zey hobn gehat a sheyne voynung.

71
00:04:16,914 --> 00:04:20,807
un mayn IMA hot oykh gehat aleyn an eygene voynung, a kleyne voynung.

72
00:04:20,924 --> 00:04:23,844
azoy arum az m'iz nisht geblibn oyf der gas.

73
00:04:24,324 --> 00:04:26,881
ober di tsayt

74
00:04:27,227 --> 00:04:29,012
iz nisht lang avek,

75
00:04:29,460 --> 00:04:34,350
efsher iz geven dray oder fir monat nokh dem vi di ershte velt-milkhome hot oysgebrokhn,

76
00:04:34,498 --> 00:04:40,497
iz mayn foter gefaln. in Pshemish, in Poyln, oyf di berg kegn di rusn,

77
00:04:40,592 --> 00:04:42,731
vayl dort iz gevezn di kamfn.

78
00:04:43,750 --> 00:04:45,627
azoy vi deys hot pasirt

79
00:04:46,249 --> 00:04:49,391
hot mayn gotzelike muter

80
00:04:49,678 --> 00:04:52,854
zikh oyfgehoybn un iz avekgeforn nokh Budapest.

81
00:04:52,986 --> 00:04:57,097
deys iz geven di ungarishe hoyptshtot demolt fun Estraykh-Ungarn.

82
00:04:57,719 --> 00:05:00,205
un zi hot zikh genumen handlen. azoy vi,

83
00:05:00,313 --> 00:05:03,481
me veyst, afile in undzere milkhomes in di ershte yorn,

84
00:05:03,564 --> 00:05:07,776
ven m'iz gekumen, iz geven UNK, az s'iz nisht geven deys, s'iz nisht geven yents,

85
00:05:07,909 --> 00:05:11,036
hot zi mit nokh andere khavertors in ir GIL

86
00:05:11,036 --> 00:05:16,869
gebrengt tsu farkoyfn mel, tsuker, farshidene zakhn. mit dem hot zi gehandlt.

87
00:05:17,094 --> 00:05:22,392
ikh bin geblibn baym SABA un der SAVTA. un mayn shvester di klenere oykh.

88
00:05:22,476 --> 00:05:26,082
baym SABA un bay SAVTA. mitn emes gezogt bin ikh kimat

89
00:05:26,082 --> 00:05:30,653
nokh dem shoyn oyfgevaksn gevorn baym SABA un SAVTA.

90
00:05:30,860 --> 00:05:32,289
un zi hot gehandlt.

91
00:05:32,463 --> 00:05:35,383
zi fleg brengen tsu farkoyfn skhoyres, un tsurikgeforn,

92
00:05:35,561 --> 00:05:41,104
un dernokhdem iz zi geven shoyn a shtik tsayt vi zi hot gehandlt in Budapest, az zi hot nisht gedarft kumen.

93
00:05:41,203 --> 00:05:50,632
ikh bin geblibn, bin gegan nokh in di ungarishe shul. ikh gedenk nisht tsi iz geven tsvey klasn, tsi dray klasn, tsi fir klasn, far mitog in shule,

94
00:05:50,790 --> 00:05:57,090
un nokh mitog in kheyder, vayl bayn undz iz geven kheyder vos me hot gelernt kinder, bay UNK.

95
00:05:57,323 --> 00:05:59,769
deys iz gevezn bay bay bay di

96
00:06:00,025 --> 00:06:06,160
 vi azoy zol ikh zogn? bay di yidishe komitet iz geven azoyne khadorim vu melamdim hobn gelernt un ikh hob dort gelernt.

97
00:06:06,652 --> 00:06:08,701
s'hot pasirt in a sheynem tog,

98
00:06:08,813 --> 00:06:12,081
kinder hobn zikh geshpilt oyf di gas, un dort vu zey zenen gegan in kheyder,

99
00:06:12,352 --> 00:06:17,949
tsi deys iz geven a kristlekh, tsi deys iz geven taken a yidish yingl, zey hobn zikh gevorfn mit shteyndlekh oyf di gas.

100
00:06:18,266 --> 00:06:21,614
umfarhoft iz gefaln mir a shteyndl in fus.

101
00:06:21,753 --> 00:06:28,315
nu, iz gefaln. ikh hob nishtamol dertseylt, ikh bin arayn tsu der SAVTA azoy vi a kind, ikh hob geveynt, ikh hob nisht gezogt gornisht.

102
00:06:28,428 --> 00:06:32,254
tsu di por teg hot mir dos ongehoybn shtark vey tun.

103
00:06:33,234 --> 00:06:35,578
di SAVTA hot gezen az epes iz nisht beseyder,

104
00:06:35,940 --> 00:06:38,591
zogt zi, "Meyer, vos hot pasirt?"

105
00:06:39,634 --> 00:06:44,698
"gornisht, a kind, vos ven." ober s'iz durkhgegan a por tog.

106
00:06:45,343 --> 00:06:51,309
deys, nisht vos s'iz geven dort a vund, nor s'iz gevorn a lekhele un se hot ongehoybn rinen eyter.

107
00:06:51,778 --> 00:06:56,118
shoyn. s'iz geven a sakh militer bayn undz, vayl in di Karpatn iz dokh gevezn di milkhome,

108
00:06:56,414 --> 00:07:00,691
iz men bald gegan tsun a militerishn dokter, ikh gedenk nokh haynt a daytshn dokter,

109
00:07:00,792 --> 00:07:07,243
di SAVTA olevasholem hot im getrogn frishe eyer, vayl s'iz geven a LUL bay der shtub,

110
00:07:07,554 --> 00:07:09,659
farn dokter, un er hot mikh bahandlt,

111
00:07:09,756 --> 00:07:11,535
un hot gegebn epes a shmir,

112
00:07:12,650 --> 00:07:16,947
un deys hot gedoyert khadoshim, un se hot zikh nisht geheylt.

113
00:07:17,034 --> 00:07:23,364
fun eyn lekhl iz gevorn efsher zeks, zibn. mayn SAVTA olevasholem hot gezen az deys iz nisht gut,

114
00:07:23,848 --> 00:07:28,769
hot zi geshribn far mayn IMA, demolt in di letste tsaytn flegt zi shoyn nisht azoy oft kumen,

115
00:07:28,905 --> 00:07:31,875
hot zi geshribn a briv, az "du muzst shnel aheymkumen

116
00:07:32,016 --> 00:07:35,421
vayl epes hot pasirt mitn kind. m'hot im gevorfn a shteyndl, do dortn."

117
00:07:35,496 --> 00:07:38,786
shoyn, zi iz gekumen, un zi hot mikh genumen

118
00:07:38,958 --> 00:07:42,769
un mitgenumen shoyn in eyn vegs di klenere shvester oykh nokh Budapest,

119
00:07:42,904 --> 00:07:47,539
azoy vi mayn foter iz shoyn geven gefaln in der milkhome, tsu di por khadoshim,

120
00:07:47,829 --> 00:07:51,649
iz demolt iz nokh nisht geven deys antisemitizm in Ungarn,

121
00:07:51,856 --> 00:07:55,630
hobn gehat a rekht di kinder fun di gefalene VÄTERs

122
00:07:56,916 --> 00:07:59,537
ontsukumen tsu doktoyrim, tsu profesorn,

123
00:07:59,719 --> 00:08:04,673
dos heyst, s'iz nokh nisht geven me zol makhn an untershid az di yidn nisht oder di ungarn yo.

124
00:08:04,889 --> 00:08:10,877
azoy arum az zi iz gevor gevorn, vayl mayn IMA hot gehat a kuzin vos er hot gevoynt dort in Budapest,

125
00:08:11,029 --> 00:08:14,805
un durkh im hot zi dortn (o) bakumen a voynung, un koydem iz s'ershte mol bayn im,

126
00:08:14,879 --> 00:08:17,500
un er hot ir gezogt vu in velkher groyser

127
00:08:17,635 --> 00:08:24,447
SPITAL, iz do dort a groyser profesor vos er bahandlt di kinder vos di VÄTERs zenen zey gefaln.

128
00:08:24,911 --> 00:08:26,621
rikhtik, s'iz azoy gevezn.

129
00:08:27,795 --> 00:08:29,441
in a sheynem tog in der fri

130
00:08:30,084 --> 00:08:32,520
hot mayn IMA, un der kuzin iz mitgekumen,

131
00:08:32,808 --> 00:08:36,768
un m'iz avekgeforn, s'iz geven zeyer vayt tsu forn mitn elektrishn

132
00:08:36,880 --> 00:08:39,821
ban oyf der gas. m'iz ongekumen ahin,

133
00:08:39,955 --> 00:08:45,117
un der profesor hot mikh bahandlt. un dervayl hot er gegebn a shmir, un er hot gezogt me zol kumen in akht tog arum,

134
00:08:45,284 --> 00:08:48,254
un nokh dem iz geven, bay di akht tog hot er gezogt me zol kumen in tsvey vokhn arum,

135
00:08:48,322 --> 00:08:54,974
biz in a sheynem tog hot er bashtimt, az me zol kumen demolt un demolt, vayl demolt darf er makhn a NITUAKH. an operatsye.

136
00:08:56,190 --> 00:08:58,711
shoyn, er iz geven zeyer ibergegebn,

137
00:08:59,388 --> 00:09:01,448
un ikh gedenk es nokh azoy vi haynt,

138
00:09:02,134 --> 00:09:05,269
ze'mir gekumen ahin, er hot mikh arayngefirt

139
00:09:05,481 --> 00:09:08,471
in operat-tsimer, vu vu me makht operatsyes,

140
00:09:08,845 --> 00:09:13,907
un aroyfgezetst oyf a tish, aropgebundn di fis, aropgebundn di hent,

141
00:09:15,493 --> 00:09:22,131
un m'hot ongehoybn tsu bakukn dem fus fun oybn arop mit farshidene shpiglen, mit farshidene dokumentn,

142
00:09:22,237 --> 00:09:24,180
un nokh a zakh vos ikh hob aykh gevolt zogn,

143
00:09:24,180 --> 00:09:30,130
az fun dem fus hot zikh gehat aropgetsoygn biz aher, un do hot zikh oykh gemakht a lekhele, se hot oykh gerunen.

144
00:09:30,407 --> 00:09:32,043
er hot gut bahandlt.

145
00:09:32,164 --> 00:09:35,525
un nokh dem iz arayngekumen tsvey shvester un zey hobn arayngebrengt

146
00:09:35,785 --> 00:09:39,276
farshidene dokumentn. un zey hobn arayngebrengt epes aza,

147
00:09:39,954 --> 00:09:46,163
azoy vi hitst iz do dey plastik, dey vos me trinkt vaser, di kinder ammeynstn teyl, aza langs,

148
00:09:46,695 --> 00:09:49,297
un er hot dos arayngeshtupt dort in dey lekhelekh.

149
00:09:50,352 --> 00:09:52,112
deys hot mikh azoy gebrent

150
00:09:53,250 --> 00:09:54,900
az ikh meyn az ikh hob geshrign

151
00:09:56,199 --> 00:09:57,969
biz untern zibetn himl.

152
00:09:58,527 --> 00:10:01,237
un er hot oysgeputst di ale lekhelekh dortn.

153
00:10:01,318 --> 00:10:04,026
un hot dos farbundn un farshmirt,

154
00:10:04,681 --> 00:10:07,850
un s'iz durkhgegan akht tog, deys hot zikh gebesert,

155
00:10:08,489 --> 00:10:12,243
tsu di dray fir khadoshim hot zikh dos plats nisht derkent.

156
00:10:12,949 --> 00:10:14,389
ad-hayom-haze,

157
00:10:15,180 --> 00:10:18,065
oysgeheylt az deys iz dort keyn mol nisht gevezn.

158
00:10:18,868 --> 00:10:21,360
ikh hob aykh gevolt fregn, vi alt zent ir demolts geven?

159
00:10:21,835 --> 00:10:23,026
umgefer,

160
00:10:23,426 --> 00:10:27,407
a a nayn yor, tsen yor, umgefer aza gatung,

161
00:10:26,662 --> 00:10:27,471
OKAY.

162
00:10:27,906 --> 00:10:30,835
a halb yor veyniker, a halb yor mer, ikh gedenk nisht.

163
00:10:29,297 --> 00:10:30,102
yo.

164
00:10:31,564 --> 00:10:33,354
deys iz geven far dem,

165
00:10:33,354 --> 00:10:37,148
vayl demolts iz nokh keyn antisetim- keyn antisemitizm nisht gevezn,

166
00:10:37,265 --> 00:10:39,901
un s'iz nisht geven keyn untershid tsi ikh bin a yidish yingl,

167
00:10:40,014 --> 00:10:41,741
tsi ikh bin a ungarish yingl.

168
00:10:41,819 --> 00:10:44,389
azoy az es hot mikh bahandlt der grester profesor.

169
00:10:45,343 --> 00:10:50,770
un der hot dos oysgeheylt biz dem hayntikn tog hob ikh m- fun dem mer nisht gevust.

170
00:10:51,231 --> 00:10:55,730
un deys iz azoy gegangen. un ze'mir shoyn geblibn voynen

171
00:10:55,803 --> 00:10:57,822
bay di IMA in Budapest.

172
00:10:58,847 --> 00:11:03,068
emes, dort bin ikh shoyn nisht gegan in shul vayl azoy vi m'iz gegan tsu dem dokter

173
00:11:03,208 --> 00:11:06,878
in BEIT-KHOLIM, m'hot gedarft geyn iberbindn, m'hot gedarft ahin un m'hot gedarft aher,

174
00:11:07,015 --> 00:11:09,150
un dos gantse voynen dort iz geven azoy

175
00:11:09,284 --> 00:11:11,482
tsaytvaylik, vayl s'iz nisht geven di heym.

176
00:11:11,552 --> 00:11:13,565
m'hot gehandlt, di IMA hot gehandlt.

177
00:11:13,700 --> 00:11:17,870
ikh gedenk nokh azoy vi haynt, se flegn aroyfkumen a sakh poylishe flikhtlingen, yidn,

178
00:11:18,126 --> 00:11:23,630
un m'hot gebrengt KARTISIM fun broyt, KARTISIM fun tsuker, un m'hot farkoyft un m'hot gemakht,

179
00:11:23,814 --> 00:11:28,206
un ikh gedenk azoy biz dem hayntikn tog az di IMA olevasholem

180
00:11:28,340 --> 00:11:33,724
fleg yedn inderfri, ven ikh un mayn shvester di kleyne flegn mir oyfshteyn,

181
00:11:34,266 --> 00:11:36,761
iz shoyn geshtanen baym bet oyf a tishele

182
00:11:37,209 --> 00:11:41,642
tsvey shtiklekh UGA far mir un far far di shvester

183
00:11:41,697 --> 00:11:44,632
vos zi hot aroyfgebrengt fun der (mehi-) fun der

184
00:11:44,854 --> 00:11:48,495
fun der tsuker-bekeray. in dem gebayde iz geven, undz ho'mir gevoynt

185
00:11:48,583 --> 00:11:50,283
in Budapest, deys iz gevezn

186
00:11:50,365 --> 00:11:53,934
lebn der yidisher gas. di yidishe gas heyst DOB-gas, DOB UTCA.

