00:11:54,019 --> 00:11:58,118
un deys iz geven di HOLLÓ-gas, numer eyns in der gebayde.

188
00:11:58,216 --> 00:12:02,284
shoyn, undz ho'mir (op)gelebt. azoy vi ober s'iz gekumen tsum sof fun der milkhome,

189
00:12:03,534 --> 00:12:06,065
hot mayn IMA nisht gevolt blaybn in Ungarn.

190
00:12:06,146 --> 00:12:08,723
tsurikforn aheym, di eltern zenen dokh dortn.

191
00:12:08,906 --> 00:12:13,200
un m'iz tsurikgeforn aheym nokh SATU MARE.

192
00:12:13,333 --> 00:12:18,780
un zi hot zikh geefnt dort a kleyn MAKOLETl, vayl zi iz shoyn geven bakont tsu farkoyfn, un tsu koyfn,

193
00:12:19,161 --> 00:12:22,857
un dos lebn iz azoy a bisl gegan vayter.

194
00:12:23,189 --> 00:12:29,433
s'hot nisht gedoyert lang, ikh veys, ikh bin shoyn alt gevorn dortn tsvelef, draytsn yor,

195
00:12:30,089 --> 00:12:32,776
un azoy vi ikh hob gezogt, mayn ABA,

196
00:12:33,106 --> 00:12:37,793
er hot gehat a finef brider oyser zikh, zenen ale gevezn oyps-sokhrim.

197
00:12:37,980 --> 00:12:43,214
un mikh hot oykh epes getsoygn, ikh hob gevolt oykhet onhoybn handlen, azoy vi ikh hob shoyn nisht gehat keyn ABA,

198
00:12:43,439 --> 00:12:47,107
un di IMA hot gehat a kleyn MAKOLETl, ikh zol ir tsuhelfn tsu der parnose.

199
00:12:47,535 --> 00:12:51,057
hot mayn SAVTA olevasholem gezogt azoy, "her oys, mayn kind:

200
00:12:51,299 --> 00:12:57,351
a soykher," zogt zi, "vestu kenen zayn ven du vest ale mol veln. ober ikh vil du zolst lernen a fakh.

201
00:12:58,622 --> 00:13:04,870
du vest hobn oysgelernt dos fakh, vos dayn harts vet zikh glustn vestu tun. ober koydem vil ikh du zolst lernen a fakh."

202
00:13:05,597 --> 00:13:10,647
lernen a fakh, hob ikh gehat a feter, mayn SAVTA hot gehat nokh a zun, dos heyst, mayner a feter,

203
00:13:10,945 --> 00:13:12,928
vos er hot gevoynt in der shtot,

204
00:13:13,327 --> 00:13:17,806
un er hot dort khasene gehat, un er hot (zikh) gemakht a gesheft fun leder

205
00:13:18,128 --> 00:13:19,353
un shteperay.

206
00:13:20,418 --> 00:13:23,436
der bester veg iz gevezn baym feter tsu lernen.

207
00:13:23,783 --> 00:13:26,789
azoy arum, az ikh bin geblibn bay dem feter,

208
00:13:27,076 --> 00:13:29,776
un ikh hob bayn im gelernt.

209
00:13:29,917 --> 00:13:33,036
un kh'hob ongehoybn tsu geyn dortn in shule,

210
00:13:33,105 --> 00:13:35,037
in der MIKTSOI-shule.

211
00:13:35,993 --> 00:13:40,181
dort hob ikh shoyn farfelt, deys vos ikh hob farfelt vos ikh hob nisht gelernt in Budapest,

212
00:13:40,271 --> 00:13:44,849
un in der heym vayl s'iz nisht gevezn, di ale lernekhts iz gevezn alts gekhapt,

213
00:13:44,849 --> 00:13:50,399
do aher un do ahin, vayl kh'bin dokh nisht geven stabil, fun der heym oyf Budapest, fun Budapest tsurik,

214
00:13:50,424 --> 00:13:51,775
un do iz di milkhome.

215
00:13:51,856 --> 00:13:54,403
azoy arum, kh'hob gelernt dort dos fakh,

216
00:13:54,939 --> 00:13:57,869
un bayn im oysgelernt,

217
00:13:58,161 --> 00:14:00,419
un nokh dem, shpeter,

218
00:14:01,294 --> 00:14:05,756
mm kh'veys, efsher mit tsvey yor, tsi mit dray yor nokh dem vi kh'hob gelernt hob ikh genumen bayn im arbetn,

219
00:14:05,899 --> 00:14:11,798
un ikh hob farkoyft in gesheft. ikh bin geven, vayl s'iz dokh geven mayn feter, s'iz dokh geven der shvester's a zun.

220
00:14:12,022 --> 00:14:13,912
azoy ikh bin geven dort oykh in der heym.

221
00:14:15,139 --> 00:14:17,237
ober ven ikh bin

222
00:14:17,795 --> 00:14:20,755
alt gevorn shoyn umgefer nayntsn,

223
00:14:21,610 --> 00:14:23,364
dakht zikh mir nayntsn yor, yo,

224
00:14:23,847 --> 00:14:26,987
ikh bin geven bafrayt fun der rumenisher armey

225
00:14:27,151 --> 00:14:32,936
vayl s'hot geheysn az ikh halt oys mayn IMA. vayl der foter iz gefaln in der milkhome

226
00:14:33,040 --> 00:14:37,010
bin ikh der oyshalter, zi hot nisht keyn andern. hob ikh in der m- armey nisht gedarft geyn.

227
00:14:37,136 --> 00:14:38,960
kh'hob gedarft makhn dort tsvey dray vokhn,

228
00:14:39,385 --> 00:14:41,481
ober deys iz geven gornisht,

229
00:14:41,762 --> 00:14:44,831
dos heyst, ikh bin geven in der heym. bay di nayntsn yor

230
00:14:45,683 --> 00:14:49,728
iz mayn ershte froy olevasholem, der froy's a shvester,

231
00:14:49,896 --> 00:14:54,785
geven in shtot bayn a kroyve dortn. un shabes,

232
00:14:54,880 --> 00:14:59,748
vos hot men getun shabes dort in shtot, in SATU MARE? s'iz geven a groyser sheyner park

233
00:15:00,015 --> 00:15:01,405
in mit shtot,

234
00:15:01,769 --> 00:15:05,895
di gesheftn dort zenen geven ale yidishe, me hot gemeynt az deys iz Yerusholaim.

235
00:15:05,953 --> 00:15:09,124
dort iz keyn kristlekh gesheft nisht geven. alts iz geven yidn.

236
00:15:09,188 --> 00:15:11,518
fleg men aroysgeyn in park un fleg dort zitsn.

237
00:15:11,627 --> 00:15:12,873
azoy m'iz gezesn,

238
00:15:12,962 --> 00:15:15,530
un zey zenen gezesn lebn a bank lebn undz.

239
00:15:15,636 --> 00:15:18,647
un nisht vilndik azoy, me heybt on tsu redn, ho'mir zikh bakent,

240
00:15:18,750 --> 00:15:22,818
un fun dem bakenekhts iz aroysgekumen der shidekh. ikh hob mit ir geheyrat.

241
00:15:22,584 --> 00:15:24,492
vi alt zent ir geven az ir hot geheyrat?

242
00:15:23,859 --> 00:15:27,340
tsvontsik yor ven ikh hob geheyrat, s'ershte mol,

243
00:15:27,969 --> 00:15:32,315
ober ober ober tsvey un tsvontsik yor, genoy ikh ken nisht khapn.

244
00:15:32,593 --> 00:15:34,360
umgefer aza gatung iz gevezn.

245
00:15:34,360 --> 00:15:37,910
ober zol ikh zogn, dray un tsvontsik?, umgefer aza gatung, ikh ken nisht...

246
00:15:38,094 --> 00:15:42,093
deys aleyn, se ligt mir nor in in in zikorn.

247
00:15:42,098 --> 00:15:42,975
beseyder.

248
00:15:43,676 --> 00:15:46,407
un kh'hob khasene gehat, un

249
00:15:46,503 --> 00:15:49,354
kh'hob geklert az ikh vel vern zelbshtendik.

250
00:15:49,705 --> 00:15:50,781
zelbshtendik.

251
00:15:52,448 --> 00:15:54,138
kh'hob mir oyfgemakht a gesheftl,

252
00:15:54,288 --> 00:15:56,546
shteperay, vayl ikh hob deys gelernt,

253
00:15:56,788 --> 00:16:00,008
un tsugenumen a mentsh, un mir ho'mir gearbet.

254
00:16:00,136 --> 00:16:02,145
un tsu bislekh iz dos gegangen.

255
00:16:02,350 --> 00:16:05,374
un nokh dem hob ikh tsugenumen nokh a mentsh, un mayn feter,

256
00:16:05,440 --> 00:16:10,321
er iz oykhet umgekumen in der milkhome, un er iz geven in Belgyum tsum sof, er iz avekgeforn,

257
00:16:10,775 --> 00:16:14,488
hot er mir gezogt, zogt er, "veystu vos?" zogt er, "az du host shoyn deys gesheftl," zogt er,

258
00:16:14,935 --> 00:16:16,978
"ikh," zogt er, "hob gehat a leder-gesheft," zogt er,

259
00:16:16,978 --> 00:16:24,003
"mit di shteperay," zogt er, "nu, iz nokh fun tsvey zaytn epes oysgekumen." zogt er, "du muzst zen, nem tsu a mentsh tsvey," zogt er,

260
00:16:24,214 --> 00:16:25,962
"vos zoln makhn shikh.

261
00:16:26,216 --> 00:16:28,078
un du vest farkoyfn shikh," zogt er,

262
00:16:28,208 --> 00:16:32,106
"vet oykh zayn a gesheft." un ikh hob azoy getun, ikh hob nokh tsugenumen tsvey mentshn,

263
00:16:32,452 --> 00:16:36,360
iz geven eyner a shteper, un eyner vos hot gemakht shikh. nokh dem hob ikh tsugenumen a ferdn.

264
00:16:36,386 --> 00:16:39,789
azoy az kimat di gantse tsayt hob ikh gearbet mit fir mentshn.

265
00:16:40,583 --> 00:16:44,763
hitst, di zakh iz azoy: afile dortn shoyn, mayn

266
00:16:45,315 --> 00:16:48,459
SABA olevasholem un di SAVTA, zey hobn gehat an eygn hoyz.

267
00:16:48,575 --> 00:16:51,871
mayn IMA hot oykh gehat, a kleyn hoyz, nisht keyn groys hoyz, a kleyn hoyz.

268
00:16:52,452 --> 00:16:55,666
hob ikh geklert, meyle a gesheftl, hob ikh gedungen dortn.

269
00:16:55,880 --> 00:17:00,246
ober tsu voynen, hob ikh geklert, vi azoy kumt men tsu tsun an eygenem hoyz?

270
00:17:00,897 --> 00:17:04,001
nu, in shtot tsu koyfn a hoyz, afile in yene tsaytn,

271
00:17:04,185 --> 00:17:06,828
in ROMÁNIA, iz geven zeyer shtark shver.

272
00:17:08,362 --> 00:17:10,403
mayn eysek iz gevezn,

273
00:17:10,476 --> 00:17:15,003
ayedn shabes in der heym, s'iz geven dort a tsaytung, se hot geheysn der SZAMOS.

274
00:17:15,079 --> 00:17:19,189
SZAMOS, deys iz geven dos vaser vos iz gegan, azoy vi s'iz do di TISZA, di Tays,

275
00:17:19,259 --> 00:17:21,191
azoy iz dort gegan der SZAMOS.

276
00:17:21,264 --> 00:17:24,486
dos iz yedn tog geven a tsaytung, un ikh fleg koyfn dem tsaytung

277
00:17:24,541 --> 00:17:30,516
un alts araynkukn, azoy vi do iz do in in MAARIV, der farkoyft un der koyft un der,

278
00:17:30,853 --> 00:17:33,397
oyf eyn mol hob ikh gezen in tsaytung

279
00:17:33,716 --> 00:17:38,439
az s'iz aroys fun der shtot an ek in der un der gas dortn, a gas,

280
00:17:38,511 --> 00:17:42,293
yene gas iz grade gegan tsu di ungarishe grenets, TISZA UNK gas,

281
00:17:42,860 --> 00:17:44,864
az dort iz do a kleyn hayzkele.

282
00:17:45,537 --> 00:17:47,437
dos hayzkl iz geven azoy groys

283
00:17:47,437 --> 00:17:50,837
vi di ershte hayzkes vos me hot geboyt do far undz in MOSHAV.

284
00:17:51,080 --> 00:17:54,575
eyn tsimerl mit a kekhl fun tsvey meter.

285
00:17:55,115 --> 00:17:58,401
az deys hayzkl iz tsu farkoyfn BEHIZDAMNUT,

286
00:17:58,669 --> 00:18:03,066
me muz nisht oyf a mol gebn dos gelt. er iz shuldik, me darf nokh epes tsoln.

287
00:18:04,226 --> 00:18:06,970
ikh hob genumen arop di adrese funem tsaytung,

288
00:18:07,176 --> 00:18:10,693
un nokh dem bin ikh tsugeforn zuntik,

289
00:18:10,693 --> 00:18:13,626
un ikh hob oyfgezukht dem, s'iz geven a goy, an ungar,

290
00:18:13,823 --> 00:18:15,806
er hot gezogt az,

291
00:18:15,920 --> 00:18:20,558
er hot ergets andersh vu tsu koyfn, er vil lebn di eltern un er vil do farkoyfn. beseyder.

292
00:18:20,851 --> 00:18:23,672
shoyn, er hot gezogt er vil far dem, in yene tsaytn,

293
00:18:23,700 --> 00:18:26,912
hot er gezogt er vil far dem tsvey un tsvontsik toyznt ley.

294
00:18:26,942 --> 00:18:28,731
in Rumenye iz geven demolt ley.

295
00:18:28,911 --> 00:18:33,847
o, s'iz geven a sakh gelt vayl fun di arbet aleyn hot men zeyer shver gekent opshporn.

296
00:18:34,827 --> 00:18:37,463
ober vos iz geven der MAZAL mayner?

297
00:18:37,926 --> 00:18:42,532
mayn zeyde olevasholem, er iz geven di gantse tsayt angeshtelt

298
00:18:42,693 --> 00:18:46,696
bay di yidishe kehile, er iz geven mashgiekh, un der

299
00:18:46,772 --> 00:18:51,279
 nu vi heyst es shoyn, shlobrik oyf yidish, oyf ivrit,...

300
00:18:51,824 --> 00:18:54,120
vu me shekht beheymes. in...

301
00:18:53,876 --> 00:18:55,592
o, in a shekht-hoyz.

302
00:18:54,999 --> 00:18:56,174
in a shekht-hoyz, yo.

303
00:18:56,174 --> 00:18:59,202
er iz geven mashgiekh di gantse tsayt, un er hot sheyn fardint,

304
00:18:59,287 --> 00:19:01,552
un s'zenen geven tsvey ire, er hot nor gehat,

305
00:19:01,552 --> 00:19:03,933
er hot gehat dray tekhter, s'iz geven mayn IMA,

306
00:19:03,933 --> 00:19:06,370
un nokh andere tsvey tekhter,

307
00:19:06,370 --> 00:19:09,749
eyne iz do geshtorbn in Erets-Yisroel vayl zi hot do, oykh do gevoynt.

308
00:19:10,524 --> 00:19:18,542
iz, bin ikh aribergegan tsum... mayn SABA, (mir zoln zikh... un) ikh hob im dertseylt, "kuk aher azoy un azoy,"

309
00:19:19,101 --> 00:19:22,410
er hot nisht gemakht keyn sakh shayles, er hot mikh gefregt vifl dos darf kostn.

310
00:19:22,422 --> 00:19:26,556
er hot aroysgenumen di helft gelt un hot mir gegebn, un er hot gezogt,

311
00:19:26,556 --> 00:19:30,371
"mayn kind, gey koyf un zay matsliekh."

312
00:19:31,020 --> 00:19:35,660
ikh bin avekgegan tsu dem, ikh hob opgehandlt nokh tsvey toyznt, kh'hob es gekoyft far tsvontsik toyznt.

313
00:19:35,660 --> 00:19:37,169
deys iz geven a kleyn hayzkl,

314
00:19:37,191 --> 00:19:38,718
ober an eygns.

315
00:19:38,868 --> 00:19:40,448
ober s'iz geven a MIGRASH,

316
00:19:40,448 --> 00:19:44,195
umgefer azoy fun finef zeks dunam, iz geven a MIGRASH.

317
00:19:44,195 --> 00:19:48,640
s'iz geven emes aroys fun der shtot, s'iz geven vayt tsu geyn, vayl ikh hob gehat in shtot dos gesheftl,

318
00:19:48,740 --> 00:19:51,914
ober ikh bin gegangen. azoy vi ikh hob deys gekoyft

319
00:19:52,273 --> 00:19:56,761
ho'mir zikh ibergetsoygn, vayl ikh hob gevoynt nisht vayt dortn in an ander gas, in (DILDISHer) gas,

320
00:19:56,852 --> 00:19:59,962
vi ikh hob gezogt, di BÁTHORY-gas, nisht vayt fun reb Yoyelishn,

321
00:20:00,030 --> 00:20:01,186
fun,

322
00:20:01,731 --> 00:20:05,657
fun Amerike vos er iz geven, er hot gevoynt dort in der gas. un

323
00:20:06,621 --> 00:20:10,051
kh'hob (oyf)gekoyft dos hayzkele, un me hot zikh ahin getsoygn,

324
00:20:10,680 --> 00:20:12,580
un ikh hob dort gevoynt.

325
00:20:13,281 --> 00:20:18,895
nu, un kh'hob getsolt tsu bislekh vos ikh hob nokh gedarft batsoln, vayl tsen toyznt hob ikh nokh gedarft batsoln.

326
00:20:19,006 --> 00:20:20,737
ober tsu bislekh fun der arbet

327
00:20:20,825 --> 00:20:26,173
hob ikh demolt, azoy vi ikh hob gehat fir mentshn, fun dem epes opgeshport, fun yenem epes opgeshport, kh'hob alts tsu bislekh batsolt.

328
00:20:26,274 --> 00:20:28,001
ven ikh hob gehat batsolt

329
00:20:29,042 --> 00:20:31,007
hob ikh geklert, vos tut men vayter?

330
00:20:31,848 --> 00:20:36,066
azoy vi ikh hob gehat dortn a MIGRASH fun finef zeks dunam,

331
00:20:36,712 --> 00:20:37,989
hob ikh

332
00:20:38,249 --> 00:20:41,325
gezogt far mayn ershte froy olevasholem,

333
00:20:41,458 --> 00:20:43,767
"veln mir boyen do ot a hoyz,

334
00:20:43,833 --> 00:20:46,580
me vet makhn a geder, me vet opteyln,

335
00:20:46,635 --> 00:20:49,126
un me vet es farkoyfn. me vet hobn gelt."

336
00:20:50,015 --> 00:20:51,149
s'iz azoy gevezn.

337
00:20:51,296 --> 00:20:53,010
tsu bislekh ho'mir genumen,

338
00:20:53,081 --> 00:20:55,989
me hot gekoyft tsu bislekh blokn, un tsu bislekh mm

339
00:20:55,989 --> 00:20:59,023
kalekh, un tsu bislekh tsigl, un tsu bislekh (dakhlkes).

340
00:20:59,062 --> 00:21:01,221
azoy arum, se hot gedoyert a tsvey yor,

341
00:21:01,255 --> 00:21:05,249
me hot oyfgeboyt dos hayzke. un ikh hob es farkoyft.

342
00:21:05,305 --> 00:21:08,219
far dem gelt vos ikh hob farkoyft deye hayzke

343
00:21:08,228 --> 00:21:12,412
hob ikh gekoyft in andern ek shtot oykhet a hoyz.

344
00:21:12,636 --> 00:21:15,324
dortn iz shoyn gevezn a gortn,

345
00:21:15,324 --> 00:21:19,972
f- oykh fun a finef dunam. mit frukht-beymer, nusn-beymer,

346
00:21:20,039 --> 00:21:22,408
in hoyf iz geven a brunem mit gut vaser,

347
00:21:22,779 --> 00:21:24,464
un a shtal,

348
00:21:24,781 --> 00:21:26,631
un ikh hob dort gekoyft.

349
00:21:27,500 --> 00:21:28,397
un,

350
00:21:29,161 --> 00:21:31,213
azoy iz gegan dos lebn vayter.

351
00:21:31,493 --> 00:21:32,862
un ikh hob gearbet.

352
00:21:33,596 --> 00:21:38,661
ober fun dem koyfn, vos ikh hob farkoyft deys hoyz, ikh hob shoyn gehat yents oysgetsolt, iz mir nokh geblibn gelt.

353
00:21:39,328 --> 00:21:40,998
demolt hob ikh ongehoybn tsu klern

354
00:21:41,728 --> 00:21:43,138
az se,

355
00:21:43,224 --> 00:21:45,396
epes darf men zen vayter tsu tun.

356
00:21:45,763 --> 00:21:48,357
a yid ken dokh ale mol nisht zitsn, er muz epes klern.

357
00:21:49,331 --> 00:21:56,115
un, in a tog, azoy vi ikh zog aykh, di tsaytung iz gekumen yedn tog, in a shabes

358
00:21:56,264 --> 00:21:59,997
ze ikh in tsaytung az se shteyt geshribn,

359
00:22:00,475 --> 00:22:02,282
ober deys iz shoyn geven umgefer,

360
00:22:02,714 --> 00:22:04,598
ah umgefer bay

361
00:22:05,357 --> 00:22:08,865
bay akht, bay akht un draysik oder zibn un draysiker yor.

362
00:22:09,575 --> 00:22:11,076
ze ikh se shteyt geshribn

363
00:22:11,448 --> 00:22:14,555
oys eyner a a krist, an ungar,

364
00:22:14,764 --> 00:22:17,299
mitn nomen SUDYETSKI,

365
00:22:17,856 --> 00:22:20,250
a general in der ungarisher armey,

366
00:22:21,030 --> 00:22:24,430
vil zeyer farkoyfn, er hot a groysn vayngortn

367
00:22:24,928 --> 00:22:26,982
vos s'iz nisht vayt fun undzer shtot.

368
00:22:27,120 --> 00:22:33,707
deys hot geheysn, oyf yidish ikh zol es iberdreyen vi azoy se hot geheysn oyf ungarish, hot dos geheysn Der Barg Fun Satmer.

369
00:22:33,870 --> 00:22:37,104
SZATMÁRHEGY, dos hot geheysn der barg fun undzer shtot.

370
00:22:37,493 --> 00:22:40,316
un dortn fun undzer shtot, fun Satmer,

371
00:22:40,378 --> 00:22:45,042
iz aroysgegan aza klener bandl vos iz geforn oyf etlekhe derfer. un ahin oykhet.

372
00:22:45,186 --> 00:22:46,342
dort oyf dem...

373
00:22:46,424 --> 00:22:48,377
az er hot dort tsu farkoyfn a vayngortn,

374
00:22:49,118 --> 00:22:55,006
halb iz a vayngortn, halb iz frukhtn farshidene, barnes, floymen, epl,

375
00:22:55,062 --> 00:22:58,486
alts iz tsu farkoyfn. un s'iz do a groyse gebayde,

376
00:22:58,727 --> 00:23:00,888
di gebayde iz gedekt mit shtroy,

377
00:23:01,077 --> 00:23:03,248
dortn in yene derfer iz geven mit shtroy,

378
00:23:03,588 --> 00:23:05,471
un helft fun der gebayde

379
00:23:05,558 --> 00:23:08,160
iz do eyn rikhtung fun makhn vayn.

380
00:23:08,347 --> 00:23:11,603
biter, shefer, mit ale farshidene zakhenes.

381
00:23:11,872 --> 00:23:14,015
un deys iz optsukoyfn nisht tayer.

382
00:23:14,166 --> 00:23:19,516
vayl er vil avekforn tsurik oyf Ungarn. er hot nisht gekent voynen in ROMÁNIA vayl er iz geven a heyser

383
00:23:19,690 --> 00:23:23,797
ungar, er iz geven an ofitsir, er iz geven a a a a (luf).

384
00:23:24,957 --> 00:23:25,643
un

385
00:23:26,307 --> 00:23:29,884
ikh bin avekgegan tsu dem in a vokhntog, ikh hob mit im geredt,

386
00:23:30,500 --> 00:23:31,266
un

387
00:23:31,977 --> 00:23:35,309
er hot gezogt, veln mir aroyfforn in a tog, ikh vel dir vayzn vos

388
00:23:35,596 --> 00:23:36,834
ikh hob tsu farkoyfn.

389
00:23:37,360 --> 00:23:39,154
er hot mikh aroyfgefirt ahin.

390
00:23:39,876 --> 00:23:43,067
un, vos zol ikh aykh zogn? azoy vi ven eyner zet epes a

391
00:23:43,237 --> 00:23:44,578
a vilde metsie,

392
00:23:44,578 --> 00:23:50,247
(ikh volt es) ven ongekhapt mit di hent un mit di tseyn. ikh zol es opkoyfn, se zol zayn mayne, vi azoy makht men es?

393
00:23:51,289 --> 00:23:56,488
er hot mikh aroyfgefirt ahin, ze'mir aroyfgeforn mitn bandl un fun dort iz men aroyfgegan umgefer

394
00:23:56,777 --> 00:24:02,296
ikh veys, efsher dray, fir hundert meter azoy oyf a barg aroyf. s'hot geheysn der shpigl-barg,

395
00:24:02,320 --> 00:24:03,712
dort vu deys iz gevezn.

396
00:24:04,116 --> 00:24:06,968
un er hot mikh arayngefirt ahin. s'iz geven a toyer gemakht

397
00:24:07,044 --> 00:24:12,332
azoy vi me zet vi dey KHAVA fun di ferd iz, fun azoyne breter, oyfgemakht dem toyer,

398
00:24:12,479 --> 00:24:16,681
arum un arum iz geven a geder-khay, fun anderthalbn meter,

399
00:24:16,744 --> 00:24:19,136
arayngefirt in dem der KHAVA.

400
00:24:19,258 --> 00:24:21,042
dort iz geven in di SHURA,

401
00:24:21,298 --> 00:24:24,291
beymer fun epl, beymer fun barnes,

402
00:24:24,712 --> 00:24:25,924
fun floymen.

403
00:24:26,030 --> 00:24:32,481
nokh dem oyf di andere zayt iz geven opgeteylt, hot zikh ongehoybn der vayngortn fun ANAVIM.

404
00:24:32,800 --> 00:24:35,684
nokh dem ze'mir tsurikgekumen, hot er arayngefirt in der shtub.

405
00:24:35,770 --> 00:24:40,798
ze'mir arayngegan, keyn podlege iz nisht gevezn. s'iz gevezn

406
00:24:41,142 --> 00:24:44,592
fun erd oyfgeshmirt, un dort hot gevoynt a goy.

407
00:24:44,905 --> 00:24:48,118
vayl oyf deye pletser hot gevoynt eyner a goy,

408
00:24:48,221 --> 00:24:55,125
far dem vos er hot dort gevoynt hot er baarbet dem gortn ven me hot gedarft. azoy iz er gegan ergets andersht oykh arbetn, un hot gearbet dort oykh.

409
00:24:55,306 --> 00:24:58,364
un er hot mir gevizn di ale zakhenes. ikh hob gezen di biter, mit dem

410
00:24:58,486 --> 00:25:01,228
(un tse)moln di vayntroybn, mit di ale zakhenes.

411
00:25:01,413 --> 00:25:03,647
se hot mir zeyer gefeln. ikh bin aroyfgekumen,

412
00:25:03,756 --> 00:25:07,042
un ikh hob dertseylt mayn ershte froy olevasholem, "kuk azoy un azoy,"

413
00:25:07,206 --> 00:25:09,821
"ober," zogt zi, "vos ken men tun, host dokh nisht keyn sakh gelt?"

414
00:25:09,936 --> 00:25:12,719
zogt zi. "der goy hot gezogt azoy," zog ikh,

415
00:25:13,029 --> 00:25:18,274
az er nemt nisht dos gantse gelt far zikh hitster mit, er hot do an advokat,

416
00:25:18,364 --> 00:25:22,278
un der advokat vet im ibershikn. kh'vel nor darfn tsoln di helft.

417
00:25:22,502 --> 00:25:29,794
di helft iz geven in yener tsayt, s'iz oykh geven a groyse metsie. s'iz geven a metsie, se hot gekost zekhtsik toyznt sh- ley.

418
00:25:30,057 --> 00:25:35,808
s'iz geven dray mol oyf azoy fil vifl di shtibl vos ikh hob gekoyft dos ershte. ober afile in dem gelt iz es geven a groyse metsie.

419
00:25:36,880 --> 00:25:39,249
shoyn, ho'mir gezogt azoy:

420
00:25:39,325 --> 00:25:43,218
ikh vel oyfnemen, s'iz geven a aza gmiles-khesed-bank far yidn

421
00:25:43,218 --> 00:25:47,062
bayn undz in shtot, un ikh hob oyfgenumen dortn tsen toyznt ley.

422
00:25:47,069 --> 00:25:49,095
ikh hob nokh gehat a tsen toyznt ley,

423
00:25:49,222 --> 00:25:55,056
un kh'hob opgekoyft deys, m'hot gemakht bayn advokat a a KHOZE,

424
00:25:55,159 --> 00:25:58,114
un me hot es arayngegebn in BET-MISHPAT,

425
00:25:58,248 --> 00:26:03,336
un ikh hob im gegebn deys gelt, un s'iz geven opgemakht az dem

426
00:26:03,421 --> 00:26:06,741
ershtn khoydesh kakh-vekakh, dem tsveytn khoydesh kakh-vekakh.

427
00:26:06,741 --> 00:26:10,466
deys iz geven umgefer, ven ikh hob es gekoyft iz geven zumertsayt,

428
00:26:10,604 --> 00:26:16,194
s'iz geven ven ven ven se hobn zikh ongehoybn di ershte frukhtn tsaytikn.

429
00:26:17,659 --> 00:26:19,540
un ikh hob es opgekoyft.

430
00:26:20,262 --> 00:26:23,640
vos zol ikh aykh zogn? yo, deys iz shoyn gevezn az me hot deys opgekoyft,

431
00:26:24,255 --> 00:26:29,340
hob ikh shoyn gehat eyn tokhter, di ershte vos iz geboyrn gevorn iz gevezn

432
00:26:30,415 --> 00:26:35,606
alt shoyn demolt bayn bayn a bayn a akht yor, nayn yor, un a zun

433
00:26:35,730 --> 00:26:39,445
hob ikh gehat vos er iz gevezn mit dray yor yinger,

434
00:26:39,627 --> 00:26:42,853
un a tsviling, meydelekh fun dray yor.

435
00:26:42,934 --> 00:26:47,419
m'hot deys opgekoyft, flegn mir koydem yedn fraytik,

436
00:26:47,493 --> 00:26:50,009
shabes iz geven geshpart vayl s'iz shabes,

437
00:26:50,090 --> 00:26:53,839
zuntik iz geven geshpart, m'hot nisht getort efenen vayl s'iz zuntik,

438
00:26:53,913 --> 00:26:57,695
flegn mir ale mol fraytik aroyfforn mit dem bandl, di gantse mishpokhe,

439
00:26:58,212 --> 00:27:00,471
afile di itstike froy mayne,

440
00:27:00,522 --> 00:27:04,211
iz oykh geven dortn, fleg aroyfkumen oyf shabes tsu helfn kloybn

441
00:27:04,241 --> 00:27:09,692
farshidene frukhtn. deys gedenkt zi nokh biz dem hayntikn tog. zi fargest a sakh zakhn ober deys gedenkt zi nokh.

442
00:27:10,208 --> 00:27:14,251
un azoy iz gegan dos lebn. ober vos ken ikh aykh zogn?

443
00:27:14,376 --> 00:27:22,733
s'iz geven, zet zikh afile nisht oyf gutn, vayl s'iz geven tsu gut, un me zogt a mol az a zakh vos iz tsu gut, dos geyt nisht tsum gutn.

444
00:27:24,445 --> 00:27:28,984
fun dem ershtn YEVUL vos dort iz gevezn in dem sod

445
00:27:29,326 --> 00:27:32,500
hob ikh oysgetsolt dem gantsn sod,

446
00:27:32,953 --> 00:27:36,388
un s'iz geven vaynen, mit frukhtn,

447
00:27:36,953 --> 00:27:38,612
nisht far di mishpokhe,

448
00:27:40,241 --> 00:27:40,979
(WE GOT TIME.)

449
00:27:40,890 --> 00:27:42,170
yo? kh'ken vayter?

450
00:27:41,928 --> 00:27:43,779
ikh vel aykh gebn a simen ven tsu oyfhern.

451
00:27:43,302 --> 00:27:43,872
yo.

452
00:27:44,732 --> 00:27:46,635
dort iz gevezn,

453
00:27:47,617 --> 00:27:48,758
s'iz gevezn,

454
00:27:49,281 --> 00:27:52,778
ikh ikh ken aykh nisht zogn, ven eyner hot dos do heyst er

455
00:27:52,906 --> 00:27:55,747
az er iz a milyoner, azoy vi me zet oyf der Riverye.

456
00:27:56,003 --> 00:27:57,551
azoyns un azelekhs.

457
00:27:57,958 --> 00:28:00,148
shoyn, ober leyder leyder,

458
00:28:00,920 --> 00:28:03,691
di goldene tsaytn hobn nisht lang gedoyert.

459
00:28:04,956 --> 00:28:09,633
di tsayt iz gegangen. m'hot gearbet. di kinder hobn gevaksn.

460
00:28:10,242 --> 00:28:11,041
un

461
00:28:12,057 --> 00:28:13,608
tsu bislekh, tsu bislekh,

462
00:28:14,002 --> 00:28:16,457
un in der tsayt,

463
00:28:16,457 --> 00:28:18,483
ikh gedenk nisht in velkhn yor,

464
00:28:18,740 --> 00:28:21,398
ober s'iz shoyn gevezn oder in,

465
00:28:21,591 --> 00:28:26,031
oder in in in in nay- oder in akht un draysiker,

466
00:28:26,485 --> 00:28:31,081
oder in nayn un draysiker, iz mayn SABA olevasholem geshtorbn.

467
00:28:32,020 --> 00:28:35,513
un s'iz geblibn... di SAVTA iz geblibn.

468
00:28:37,561 --> 00:28:42,015
s'hot nisht gedoyert lang di tsaytn, di milkhome hot zikh ongefangen.

469
00:28:43,590 --> 00:28:47,368
yetst veln mir do oyfhe- -hern, mir'n toyshn a kasete un me vet geyn foroys.

